SELECT SERVER NUMBER TO RECEIVE EVENT

This screen is used to raise the database event selected in the Send
Database Event screen to one or all of the servers that are currently
running against the local database.

The column on the list is:

        COLUMN NAME     DESCRIPTION
        -----------     -----------
        Server Number   The number of a server to receive the event.


The menu commands are as follows:

        MENU COMMAND    SYNOPSIS
        ------------    --------
        Send            Send the event to the currently highlighted
                        server number.

        All             Send the event to all the currently running
                        servers.

        Help            Access the Help facility.

        End             Return to the Send Database Event screen.
